TITLE:: Approximation Algorithms for the Minimum Bends Traveling Salesman Problem
TYPE:: Technical Report (paper)
REVISION:: 1
AUTHOR:: Stein, Cliff
AUTHOR:: Wagner, David P.
DATE:: April 2000
RETRIEVAL:: For a paper copy, email <reports@cs.dartmouth.edu>
