TITLE:: Relaxing the Problem-Size Bound for Out-of-Core Columnsort
TYPE:: Technical Report (paper)
REVISION:: 1
AUTHOR:: Chaudhry, Geeta
AUTHOR:: Hamon, Elizabeth A. 
AUTHOR:: Cormen, Thomas H. 
