TITLE:: Classifying the Mobility of Users and the Popularity of Access Points
TYPE:: Technical Report (paper)
REVISION:: 1
AUTHOR:: Kim, Minkyong
AUTHOR:: Kotz, David
DATE:: May 2005
RETRIEVAL:: For a paper copy, email <reports@cs.dartmouth.edu>
