TITLE:: The Theory of Trackability with Applications to Sensor Networks
TYPE:: Technical Report (paper)
REVISION:: 1
AUTHOR:: Crespi, Valentino
AUTHOR:: Cybenko, George V.
AUTHOR:: Jiang, Guofei
DATE:: August 2005
