TITLE:: Secure Context-sensitive Authorization 
TYPE:: Technical Report (paper)
REVISION:: 1
AUTHOR:: Minami, Kazuhiro
DATE:: February 2006	
RETRIEVAL:: For a paper copy, email <reports@cs.dartmouth.edu>
RETRIEVAL:: For a paper copy, write to
