TITLE:: Fast-Converging Tatonnement Algorithms for the Market Problem
TYPE:: Technical Report (paper)
REVISION:: 1
AUTHOR:: Cole, Richard
AUTHOR:: Fleischer, Lisa
DATE:: August 2007
RETRIEVAL:: For a paper copy, email <reports@cs.dartmouth.edu>
