TITLE:: LZfuzz: a fast compression-based fuzzer for poorly documented protocols
TYPE:: Technical Report (paper)
REVISION:: 1
AUTHOR:: Bratus, Sergey
AUTHOR:: Hansen, Axel
AUTHOR:: Shubina, Anna
DATE:: September 2008
EMBARGO:: month day year (optional; TR will not be released until this date)
