TITLE:: Constant RMR Solutions to Reader Writer Synchronization
TYPE:: Technical Report (paper)
REVISION:: 1
AUTHOR:: Bhatt, Vibhor
AUTHOR:: Jayanti, Prasad
DATE:: February 2010
RETRIEVAL:: For a paper copy, email <reports@cs.dartmouth.edu>
