TITLE:: Exploring the Use of I/O Nodes for Computation in a MIMD Multiprocessor
TYPE:: Technical Report (paper)
REVISION:: 3
AUTHOR:: Kotz, David
AUTHOR:: Cai, Ting
NOTE:: The 'January' in DATE is an arbitrary placeholder.
DATE:: January 1994
